Hi. Thanks for the recording.

I wondered if you could upload a version that was encoded better. Using 128kbps with 8kHz mono is redundant, one can hear the digital processing artifacts really well...

At that rate (128kbps), you could have very well used 44,1kHz stereo.

But 8kHz is definitely too low...
